This simplifies to:

\begin{align*}
x^3+x^2+2x^2-3x^2+3x-6
\end{align*}

Combine like terms:

\begin{align*}
x^3+0x^2+3x-6
\end{align*}

So the simplified expression is \(\boxed{x^3+3x-6}\).

